728809f-a.title: Richmond: Edgewater Street - Sylva Lane
728809f-a.text:
EAgewater Street (foregr und), east side, at the foot of Sylva Lane, showing the boat house of the Clifton Boat Club, on the Upper New York Bay. Also shown are several freighters
tied up to one of the wharves.
1924
P. L. Sperr
